Body: Yumerium launches Win-Win event during main sale; Refer to Earn Tokens https://bitcoingarden.org/yumerium-launches-win-win-event-during-main-sale/  With six games up and running, the Yumerium gaming platform just launched a main sale on September 26 along with a Win-Win event. Users referring the sale get a chance to earn tokens based on the referred investment. Furthermore, those participating through the referral link get an additional 10% bonus in tokens. Both the main sale and ‚ÄúWin-Win‚Äù event will run until October 10, 2018.  The Win-Win event is limited to Ethereum investments only. Participants will pay a small gas fee and get a referral link at yumerium.com/tokensales. Then, they can simply spread out the referral link to get the referred investment.  Yumerium is a blockchain-based gaming platform where players can earn tokens by sharing, reviewing, and playing. The newly launched game will showcase this fundamental mechanism of earning tokens by playing games. Through the smart contract that is already built on the ‚ÄòStore‚Äô page, users can simply download the games and play to get tokens on the website using blockchain technology....

Author: Kuala Lumpur
Title: [ANN] YUMERIUM - AN INCENTIVIZED, BLOCKCHAIN BASED, OPEN GAMING PLATFORM üïπÔ∏èüïπÔ∏è
Body: ICO Analysis: Yumerium Published on August 24, 2018 By Daniel Won Proof: https://hacked.com/ico-analysis-yumerium/  Team Founder and CEO Jikhan Jung: Jung has worked in several VR companies, such as Subdream Studios where he is the current CEO and VR Plus, a VR gaming company. CTO Francisco Martin: Martin is the CTO at Subdream Studios and has worked as a game director at Virtual World Arcade. CSO Jaehyun Lee: Lee, the former CEO at Super Bee and Zen Software, is the current CEO at Hurbit, a cryptocurrency exchange. Advisors Koji Sakamoto: Sakamoto is the former managing director at Excite Japan, CEO at YJ America and a former corporate officer at Yahoo! Japan. He is currently the board director at TBM Co., Ltd. Partners VR Plus: The biggest VR arcade franchise in Korea will act as a distribution partner. Subdream Studios: A California-based game developer.  Verdict Below is a breakdown of the risks and growth potential of Yumerium.  Risks     Historically speaking, gaming platform ICOs do not have good ROI. (-1)     No to small marketing campaign so far, resulting in low community interest. (-2)  Growth Potential     Though gaming platform ICOs usually fail to meet expectations, they get a lot of interest from the crowd. (+1.5)     Aims to provide most of Steam‚Äôs and Kickstarter‚Äôs features with some additional ones. Allowing players to resell owned games is definitely a good move. (+2.5)     Allocating some tokens for Marketing Fund to incentivize developers to use Yumerium might create great interest in the project. (+1.5)     A good blockchain gaming platform is much needed. (+1)  Disposition Yumerium is essentially a gaming platform, sharing many features with Steam and Kickstarter. Although gaming platform ICOs historically do not do well, Yumerium still might attain serious attraction from both gamers and developers if they execute a great marketing campaign. Yumerium receives a 5/10.  Investment Details     Type: ERC20 ‚Äì Utility     Symbol: YUM     Platform: Ethereum     Crowdsale: September 26, 2018     Minimum Investment: 0.1 ETH     Price: $0.01     Hard Cap: $20,000,000     Payments Accepted: ETC, BTC     Restricted from Participating: China, USA

Title: [ANN] YUMERIUM - AN INCENTIVIZED, BLOCKCHAIN BASED, OPEN GAMING PLATFORM üïπÔ∏èüïπÔ∏è
Body: Dear Yumerians,  How To Participate In Yumerium Public Pre-Sale Round 1  Token sale page: https://yumerium.com/buytoken1  Here We Go. Step-by-Step.  Step 1 - Fill out the form and upload KYC (Know Your Customer) information. This ensures nobody cheats and buys more than allowed by making multiple accounts.  Step 2 - Verify your email. If you can't find it, make sure to look in your spam folder. The email will include a link to the token purchase page.  Step 3 - Choose if you'd like to contribute using ETH or BTC and the amount. - For ETH, after the transaction is successful, you'll get your YUM automatically! Please make sure that you wallet allows you to add ERC20 tokens. - For BTC, you will receive a BTC wallet to transfer funds to. Unfortunately, this process isn't automatic, so after your transaction is verified, you will receive YUM within 3 days.  Step 4 - Click Participate and you're done! You can start using YUM in the Yumerium store. The store uses the MetaMask extension for simpler YUM transfers. You can download the extension at https://metamask.io/. We have many announcements for new games coming soon to the platform, along with other places you can use YUM.

Author: S3cco
Title: [ANN] YUMERIUM - AN INCENTIVIZED, BLOCKCHAIN BASED, OPEN GAMING PLATFORM üïπÔ∏èüïπÔ∏è
Body: Bitcoin Garden: Blockchain Platform Yumerium Set to Change the Gaming Market https://bitcoingarden.org/blockchain-platform-yumerium-set-to-change-the-gaming-market/  Yumerium is a next-gen, decentralized gaming platform that integrates payments, game development, and community participation by gamers worldwide into one comprehensive solution to overcome long-standing issues in online gaming such as fraud, high transaction fees, and delayed payments.  The platform runs on a native token called YUM, which can be earned by playing, sharing, and reviewing games. By supporting transactions made in YUM, Yumerium provides an easier and more efficient way for game developers and studios to create and market games. This allows them to more easily grow their active users and overall brand. Gamers also benefit from lower costs and the ability to earn while playing the games they love.  The world‚Äôs media and entertainment market is worth an estimated 1.7 trillion dollars. With consistent double-digit growth year on year for the past decade or so, this market is expected to hit a value of 2.2 trillion dollars over the next three years.  Gaming is an integral segment of the global entertainment market and it currently has a value of roughly 110 billion dollars. The world‚Äôs largest gaming regions are Asia Pacific and North America, and these two regions account for over 75 percent of global gaming revenues. Within general gaming, online gaming has seen particularly explosive growth, as can be inferred from the fact that digital gaming sales outperform physical game sales by a factor of 3. With a global gamer population of over one billion (with 70% of them playing online games), these statistics prove one thing: online gaming is, to put it very simply, a market with immeasurable potential....

Author: Vladdirescu87
Title: [ANN] YUMERIUM - AN INCENTIVIZED, BLOCKCHAIN BASED, OPEN GAMING PLATFORM üïπÔ∏èüïπÔ∏è
Body: Yumerium: From ‚ÄúPay-to-Play‚Äù to ‚ÄúEarn-to-Play‚Äù  Yumerium is a new ecosystem of several games that allow you gamers, publishers and developers to earn. Today it is built around the game CryptoMine‚Ää‚Äî‚Ääa strategy in which you will need to build factories for the extraction of precious stones. Participants receive income, participate in lotteries for the distribution of ‚Äúlegendary stones‚Äù with special value. In future, each developer will be able to post their games on the Yumerium platform.  Each game will be initially placed with ‚Äúseeding funds‚Äù in the form of YUM currency, which developers can spend on marketing, in order to attract players to a new game. In the future, gamers will be able to earn (or ‚Äúget‚Äù) YUM tokens playing, inviting other players or posting reviews about the game.  YUM tokens will be accepted in all games on the Yumerium platform. The authors of the project expect that with the passage of time the number of games will increase significantly.  Read more: https://medium.com/@Vladar49/yumerium-from-pay-to-play-to-earn-to-play-e54c139d94a1
